data.description: Looking for a secluded home without being too far away from all the amenities of a small town?  Look no further than this great 3 bedroom, 1 bath ranch located in Pleasant Prairie!  Nestled on less than an acre lot, this one owner home is ready for your finishing touches!  It includes a great 3 car garage, storage shed, and beautifully landscaped yard!  Schedule your showing today!
